These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: chess, domino, poker
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, colombian, brazilian
3 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing chess is between the colombian and the brazilian##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Game         | domino | chess   | poker   |
| Nationality   | colombian     | malaysian | brazilian |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | ferret    | fish      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, blend, dannemann
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, gospel, soul
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, chef, lawyer
City: paris, prague, berlin
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the lawyer is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the blend-smoker is the lawyer##1
4. the havana-smoker is the chef##1
5. the person traveling to paris is between the fan of gospel and the dannemann-smoker##2
6. the dannemann-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Cigar          | blend  | havana     | dannemann     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | soul     | blues      |
| Job   | lawyer  | chef | pilot |
| City           | berlin | paris     | prague       |

