.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
City: london, nizza, prague
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, paramedic
House: cottage, townhouse, palace
3 different games are played: poker, snooker, canasta
1. the bartender is on the left of the palace house##1
2. the person playing poker is between the paramedic and the palace house##2
3. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
4. the person playing snooker is the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person playing poker is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| City          | london  | prague     | nizza     |
| Job           | paramedic | bartender  | doctor   |
| House   | cottage  | townhouse    | palace |
| Game           | canasta     | poker | snooker |

