.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, poker, canasta
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, purple, lilac
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, water
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person playing canasta is between the paramedic and the person who likes red##2
4. the person playing poker is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Game    | monopoly       | canasta  | poker   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Color     | purple   | lilac | red        |
| Beverage   | water | cola     | sprite      |

