.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, game, fonseca
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, may, august
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, indonesian, thai
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the indian is between the person who's birthday is in august and the fonseca-smoker##2
3. the baccarat-smoker is the indonesian##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the indian is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Cigar         | baccarat | game | fonseca |
| Birthday   | august  | may       | december       |
| Nationality           | indonesian     | indian       | thai     |

