2. the person eating pumpkin is the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person watching musical movies is between the person eating pineapple and the librarian##2
4. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | pumpkin    |
| Cigar         | blend | vegafina      | montecristo |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | musical     | animation        |
