.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold, zinnia
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, musician, teacher
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, rowing, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the musician is between the person who growszinnia and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
5. the musician is between the teacher and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Flower          | zinnia      | marigold   | begonia |
| Job         | paramedic | musician | teacher |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Sport     | surfing         | rowing  | swimming       |

