.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, spy
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, tiparillo-climbing
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, apricot, grey
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, tiparillo
1. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who likes ivory is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person watching spy movies##2
5. the person watching documentary movies is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Movie-Genre      | crime       | documentary      | spy      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | tiparillo-climbing | chess      |
| Color           | grey | ivory     | apricot |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | tiparillo          | aristoff       |

