There 3 different types of food: carrot, papaya, peas
City: nizza, hannover, paris
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, collecting, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to paris##2
2. the person eating peas is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
4. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Pet      | pony      | ferret | hedgehog     |
| Food          | papaya   | carrot      | peas     |
| City   | paris  | nizza      | hannover |
| Hobby     | hiking | puzzles        | collecting     |

