The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, engineer, librarian
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the librarian##1
3. the engineer is in the middle##1
4. the engineer is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
