The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, daffodil
1. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Transport      | subway | roller      | bus            |
| Hobby           | fishing | cooking | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| Flower   | marigold  | amaryllis    | daffodil        |

