2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the person eating garlic is the oliveros-smoker##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Music-Genre      | rock    | disco          | indie |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Game           | go | scrabble | bridge         |
| Cigar   | chaman    | dunhill    | oliveros      |

