The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, july, april
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, photographer, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, thriller, animation
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the photographer##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is between the person who's birthday is in april and the police-officer##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
| Birthday   | april  | july     | february |
| Job   | bartender | photographer | police-officer   |
| Movie-Genre     | animation   | thriller   | scientific      |

