3. the chaman-smoker is the person who growsiris##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to paris is between the person traveling to prague and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| City           | new-york   | paris   | prague |
