.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
City: liverpool, new-york, colone
House: art-deco, victorian, wooden
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, brown, orange
1. the person who likes brown is the wooden house##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the art-deco house is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person traveling to liverpool##2
4. the victorian house is the person who likes orange##1
5. the person who likes coral is between the person drinking milk and the victorian house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| City         | new-york   | colone | liverpool |
| House   | victorian        | art-deco       | wooden      |
| Color           | orange           | coral    | brown       |

